<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1039093" n="1"/> 
  <opener><salute><rs key="pers_DE-588-1132220874" type="person">Jeremiae Raillardo</rs> Amico suo perdilecto</salute> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nic. Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs></opener>
  <p><lb/>Gratissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ae mihi fuerunt <rs type="letter">liter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, Amice charissime, non solum quod ad <rs type="letter">literas meas</rs> tam cito
    <lb/>respondere voluisti, <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>ob quod tamen tibi non parvas ago gratias<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> sed etiam et quidem pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue quod
    <lb/>mihi spem injecisti, tres cameras in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dibus vestris <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> tribus <rs type="person">Tigurinis</rs> hactenus inhabitatas intra octi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>duum evacuatum iri, quarum unam Te ipsum occupaturum esse nuntiasti, ex reliquis igitur dua<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus ego forte, si contigerit me salvum et incolumem <rs key="place_GEO-2660646" type="place">Genevam</rs> venire, unam mihi sumam, tuoque
    <lb/>contubernio l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus fruar, nec me absterrebit quod alia hospitia pro decem tantum thaleris men<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>struis venalia sint, cum tamen vos <rs type="person">Sarasin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> vestr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> duodecim solvatis, nam consortium tuum
    <lb/>et gaudia, quibus in conversatione tua fruiturus sum, longe pluris <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimo quam duos
    <lb/>thaleros menstruos. Nondum tamen pro certo affirmare possum, me Tuo hospitio usurum esse,
    <lb/>nam <rs type="person">amicus</rs> quidam Basiliensis nuper per <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs> <rs type="person">mercatorem</rs> quendam Genevensem, qui
    <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-135542286" type="person">Patrem meum</rs> et me ipsum bene novit, rogavit, ut me in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>des suas recipere aut aliud hospitium
    <lb/>mihi qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>rere vellet; quod si igitur nullum adhuc hospitium meo nomine conduxit, tuum
    <lb/>omnibus aliis pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>feram. Diem adventus mei, et an equum <rs key="place_GEO-2661552" type="place">Berna</rs> adducturus sim, nondum
    <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dicere possum, hoc tamen certum est, <rs type="person">Bernenses</rs> quosdam <rs type="person">studiosos</rs> intra decendium
    <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-2660646" type="place">Genevam</rs> profecturos esse, quos ego comitabor, nisi alia co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>dior occasio sese mihi obtu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lerit. <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089804180" type="person">D. Falcisium</rs> et <rs key="pers_DE-588-1072469103" type="person">Beckium</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-2660646" type="place">Genevam</rs> relicturos esse, haud l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus intellexi, causam hu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>jus abitus valde scire laboro, nam vix credere possum, illum Diaconatui, quo hactenus
  <pb facs="1039094" n="2"/> 
    <lb/>functus est, et hunc studiis Juridicis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> nuper <rs key="place_GEO-2660646" type="place">Genev<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> resumsit, tam cito iterum valedixisse. Ut <rs key="pers_DE-588-140736662" type="person">Christius</rs> quo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que noster <rs key="place_GEO-2660646" type="place">Genevam</rs> inviseret, valde optarem, et me voti mei compotem fore sperarem, nisi scirem
    <lb/>Examen Juridicum, cui se fortasse brevi tempore submittet, in pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sens illum <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> retinere; spero
    <lb/>me hodie <rs type="letter">literas</rs> ab ipso accepturum esse mediante <rs type="person">famulo</rs> <rs type="person">Thurnisii</rs>, qui cum aliis <rs type="person">Bibliopolis</rs> ad nun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dinas proxime instantes hodie veniet. </p><closer>Vale. <dateline><rs key="place_GEO-2661552" type="place">Bern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1710-04-27">27. Aprilis 1710</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
